{"article_id":"W1FrXWRSCms3g4q0","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hurricane Florence was downgraded to Category 2 late Wednesday night","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"but remained a clear danger to the East Coast with `` life-threatening '' storm surge and rainfall in the forecast .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"As expected ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"Florence has slowed on its approach to North Carolina and South Carolina ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"where it 's expected to make landfall late Thursday or early Friday ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"bombarding communities with torrential rain , high winds and deadly storm surge until Saturday .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Hurricane winds could linger for 24 hours or more ,","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"sweeping away trees and power lines","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"while dumping 20 to 30 inches of rain in some coastal areas ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"the National Hurricane Center","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"( NHC )","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"said .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Isolated totals of 40 inches are possible .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Florence was driving sustained winds of 110 mph on Wednesday night","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and , earlier in the day , had created waves up to 83 feet ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"the hurricane center said ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"with the first tropical winds sweeping ashore before noon .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The approach of Florence has put more than 10 million people under storm watches and warnings across three states .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Along the coasts areas , more than 1 million people have been ordered to evacuate .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Duke Energy warned","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that up to 75 percent of its 4 million customers in the Carolinas could lose power .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"`` This is not going to be a glancing blow , ''","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Federal Emergency Management Agency 's Jeff Byard said .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"`` This is going to be a Mike Tyson punch to the Carolina coast . ''","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"'Storm of a lifetime ' :","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"storm surge , extreme winds and torrents of rain","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"The storm , as of 11 p.m. EDT , was about 280 miles east-southeast of Wilmington , North Carolina , and 325 miles east-southeast of Myrtle Beach , South Carolina ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"moving northwest at 17 mph .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The National Weather Service in Wilmington warned","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that Florence `` will likely be the storm of a lifetime for portions of the Carolina coast . ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"The NHC stressed","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that tropical-storm force winds","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"arriving Thursday morning","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"would make outside preparations `` difficult or dangerous . ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"`` Preparations","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"to protect life and property","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"should be rushed to completion , ''","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"the NHC bulletin warned .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"After an earlier flirtation with up the coast toward Virginia , the southern turn brings Georgia into the path of the storm .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Gov . Nathan Deal declared an emergency Wednesday for all 159 counties .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"But North Carolina remained a primary target ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and Gov . Roy Cooper has ordered an unprecedented evacuation of the state 's barrier islands .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"The storm surge alone will flood tens of thousands of structures ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"Cooper said Wednesday .","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"`` Every county and every person in North Carolina needs to stay alert","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"and to take this storm seriously , ''","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"Cooper said .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Not everyone was fleeing .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"In Wilmington , James Waters said","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"he surfed Wednesday morning","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"and was going to stay at his grandparents ' house just across the water from the islands .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"\" My grandparents are staying ,","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"so I figured","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"I would stay","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"and help them , \"","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"Waters said .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"\" We ' ve been through some hurricanes before .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"They say","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"this one is supposed to be really bad . \"","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"President Donald Trump again warned people to heed storm warnings on Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Hurricane Florence `` is going to be one of the biggest ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to ever hit the East Coast or the United States as a whole .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"There is `` a big situation","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"confronting us , ''","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Trump said during a White House reception for Congressional Medal of Honor recipients and their families .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"his administration is in close contact with state and emergency management officials .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Outside Wilmington , less than two miles from the coast , the Trinity Grove nursing home has stocked extra food , medicine and water for some 100 residents ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"who will shelter in place .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"The facility was built","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"to withstand 140 mile per hours wind ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"says John Frye , the executive director .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Kay Torrens , 88 ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"who has lived for 25 years in Trinity Grove with her 87-year-old husband , Leo ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"says","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"she is heading to Virginia","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to stay with relatives ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"leaving the facility for the first time ever","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"- and without Leo .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"\" He ' s in good hands .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Why would I not trust it ? \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Torrens said .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" I wouldn ' t leave him","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"if it wasn ' t safe . \"","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Weather Channel meteorologist Greg Postel said","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Florence has an unusual forecast track .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"`` I 've never seen anything like this , ''","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Ryan Maue , a meteorologist at weather.us","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Florence is forecast to dump about 10 trillion gallons of water on the Carolinas ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"called the forecast `` bizarre ''","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"`` the forecast after 72 hours is certainly a challenge ... and a nightmare . ''","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Despite Florence ' s southern turn ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"people as far as Norfolk , Virginia , fled to higher ground .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Wilma Johnson was on her way out of town Wednesday morning","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"after her neighborhood","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"that abuts the Elizabeth River","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"was ordered evacuated by Gov . Ralph Northam .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"But she was having second thoughts .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"\" I ' m not really afraid , \"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"I ' d be much more comfortable at home . \"","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"The new track could make a tremendous difference to residents of the Washington , D.C. , metro area and points north .","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Alan Reppert , a senior meteorologist for AccuWeather , said","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"areas around Richmond , Virginia , could see 8 inches of rain .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"Washington , 100 miles to the north , might get only an inch .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"FEMA ready to respond to Florence","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"despite cash transfer to ICE","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"'Take your pets with you ' during and after Hurricane Florence","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"Travel disruptions will be many .","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"Nationwide , more than 575 flights have been canceled from Wednesday through Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"flight-tracking service FlightAware reported .","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"Amtrak canceled some trains","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"and modified service for others in the region","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"and announced","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"its Northeast Regional service will not run to Virginia destinations south of Washington from Wednesday through Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"President Donald Trump lauded FEMA for its work during last year 's devastating hurricane season","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"authorities were ready for Florence .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"`` Hurricane Florence is looking even bigger","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"than anticipated , ''","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"`` It will be arriving soon .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"FEMA , First Responders and Law Enforcement are supplied and ready .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Be safe ! ''","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Contributing :","depth":2},{"id":133,"text":"Doyle Rice , Ledyard King , Sean Rossman and Ben Mutzabaugh , ; Daniel Gross , of The Greenville News , reported from Wilmington .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":267,"left":265,"right":266,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":244,"right":264,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":219,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":193,"right":218,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":193,"left":150,"right":192,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":135,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":145,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":138,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":137,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":136,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":143,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":140,"right":142,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":6,"right":139,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":141,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":146,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":159,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":156,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":151,"righ